<blockquote>
<p><span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>ϵ</mi><mi>l</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\epsilon_l</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.5806em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal">ϵ</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3361em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.01968em;">l</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 的選擇根據 <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/1803.00933" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Dan Horgan, John Quan, David Budden, et al. (2018)<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> 如下</p>
<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>ϵ</mi><mi>l</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>ϵ</mi><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mi>α</mi><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow><mi>L</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfrac></mrow></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">
